data.description:
UPDATE: Buyer can now enjoy an additional $4,000 in sellers credit to be used towards updates, rate buy-downs, etc.*.  Situated near shopping, dining, rivers and lakes, this 4 bedroom home is as conveniently located as you'll find anywhere! This large 2700 square foot home has just received brand new carpets in 3 bedrooms.  Located on a quaint cul-de-sac, this home has access to excellent neighborhood amenities to include a pool, basketball courts, and walking trail.   
Large game/flex room, 2-car garage, dedicated laundry room, and plenty of backyard privacy with a fresh 6' privacy fence along all sides.  Centrally located and priced to sell, this versatile home is a blank canvas, ready to make your own.
*Seller may credit the Buyer up to $4,000 at closing in the form of seller concessions IF allowable by the lender, if financing is used.
